        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4599",
        "content": "\"For I do believe a great part of it's liver or nerves!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4599_21274_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4599/21274/4599_21274_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4599",
        "content": "So she submitted, and presently learnt, under dire stress of boredom, to amuse herself a good deal by developing a natural capacity for dreaming awake.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4599_21274_000036_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4599/21274/4599_21274_000036_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4599",
        "content": "Then, when the Princess had held out a gracious hand and smiled, all was delight!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4599_21274_000038_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4599/21274/4599_21274_000038_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4599",
        "content": "Even at ten years old she perfectly understood that she was one of the Boyces of Brookshire, and that her great uncle had been a famous Speaker of the House of Commons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
